#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/040_Three_Essential_Tools.md:408
msgid ""
"we can spot that these values are not used anywhere -- the tested class "
"does not use or check them in any way. These values are important from "
"the database point of view, but we already took the real database out of "
"the picture. Doesn't it trouble you that we fill the order object with so"
" many values that are irrelevant to the test logic itself and that "
"clutter the structure of the test with needless details? To remove this "
