#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/255_Value_Objects_properties.md:292
msgid ""
"and all our code depends on it for creating product names rather than on "
"the constructor, we are free to make the `ProductName` class abstract at "
"some point and have the `For()` method return an instance of a subclass "
"of `ProductName`. This change would impact just this static method, as "
