#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:9
msgid ""
"The first factory is for creating instances of `ReservationInProgress` --"
" remember? You gave it a bogus name on purpose. Look:"
msgstr "La prima factory serve per creare istanze di `ReservationInProgress` -- ricordi? Gli hai dato un nome strano apposta. Guarda:"

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:21
msgid "**Johnny:** Oh, yeah, that one..."
msgstr "**Johnny:** Oh, sì, quello..."

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:23
msgid ""
"**Benjamin:** and the second factory is for creating commands -- it's "
"called `TicketOfficeCommandFactory`:"
msgstr "**Benjamin:** e la seconda factory serve per creare comandi -- si chiama `TicketOfficeCommandFactory`:"

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:37
msgid "**Johnny:** Let's do this one."
msgstr "**Johnny:** Facciamolo."

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:39
msgid "**Benjamin:** Why this one?"
msgstr "**Benjamin:** Perché questo?"

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:41
msgid ""
"**Johnny**: No big reason. I just want to dig into the domain logic as "
"soon as possible."
msgstr "**Johnny**: Nessun motivo in particolare. Voglio solo approfondire la logica del dominio il prima possibile."

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:43
msgid ""
"**Benjamin**: Right. We don't have a Specification for this class, so "
"let's create one."
msgstr "**Benjamin**: Giusto. Non abbiamo una Specifica per questa classe, quindi creiamone una."

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:52
msgid ""
"**Johnny**: Go on, I think you will be able to write this Statement "
"mostly without my help."
msgstr "**Johnny**: Continua, penso che sarai in grado di scrivere questo Statement senza il mio aiuto."

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:54
msgid ""
"**Benjamin**: The beginning looks easy. I'll add a new Statement which I "
"don't know yet what I'm going to call."
msgstr "**Benjamin**: L'inizio sembra facile. Aggiungerò un nuovo Statement  che non so ancora come chiamerò."

#: ../../TddEbook_Sphinx/source/manuscript/310_Test_Driving_Factories.md:67
msgid ""
